程序包 org.apache.hadoop.registry.server

程序包org.apache.hadoop.registry.server的说明

Server-side classes for the registry

These are components intended to be deployed only on servers or in test JVMs, rather than on client machines.

Example components are: server-side ZK support, a REST service, etc.
